name: MeatTemp
0:
”Alexa, ask Meat Temp What is the internal temperature for steak?”
”Alexa, ask Meat Temp what temperature do you serve chicken?”
”Alexa, ask Meat Temp what temperature do I cook ground beef to?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: meat temp
des:
By asking Meat Temp you can find out the suggested temperature to cook different meats to. Currently we support Shell Fish, Fish, Ground Beef, Steak, Turkey and Chicken. Please note that we are not liable for any consumption of raw or undercooked meats, these are just suggestions from the internet.
